==票房==
澳大利亚收获435万美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=animalkingdom.htm |title=Animal Kingdom (2010) - International Box Office Results |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=30 January 2011 |archive-date=2010-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100825181452/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=animalkingdom.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，为2010年度澳洲票房第三高电影。全球累计577万美元<ref name="boxofficemojo1"/>。

==奖项==
影片获得澳洲电影学院奖12项提名，赢得最佳影片、导演、编剧、男主角（Ben Mendelsohn）、女主角（Jacki Weaver）、男配角（Joel Edgerton）在内的7个奖<ref>{{cite news |first=Luke |last=Dennehy |url=http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/movies/melbourne-crime-thriller-animal-kingdom-earns-nine-afi-gongs/story-e6frfmvr-1225969545998 |title=Melbourne crime thriller Animal Kingdom earns ten AFI gongs |publisher=News.com.au |date=12 December 2010 |accessdate=30 January 2011 |archive-date=2016-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130135813/http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/movies/melbourne-crime-thriller-animal-kingdom-earns-nine-afi-gongs/story-e6frfmvr-1225969545998 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Jacki Weaver还获得[[第68届金球奖|第68届金球奖]]和[[第83届奥斯卡金像奖|第83届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳女配角提名。

[[国家评论协会|国家评论协会]]将其评为年度最佳[[独立电影|独立电影]]之一<ref name="NBR">{{cite web |url=http://www.altfg.com/blog/movie/david-fincher-the-social-network-national-board-of-review-awards-2010/ |title=David Fincher's THE SOCIAL NETWORK Tops National Board of Review Awards 2010 |publisher=ALT Film Guide |accessdate=30 January 2010 |archive-date=2012-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001195806/http://www.altfg.com/blog/movie/david-fincher-the-social-network-national-board-of-review-awards-2010/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

